results.name: Number of parts in all partitions of n with largest multiplicity eight.
link: Alois P. Heinz, Table of n, a(n) for n = 8..1000
formula: a(n) ~ log(3) * exp(4*Pi*sqrt(n/3)/3) / (Pi * sqrt(2) * 3^(1/4) * n^(1/4)). - _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Oct 25 2018
